1 large head cabbage, finely chopped
14.5 oz can tomatoes with juice
1 onion, halved and thinly sliced
1 Tbsp Italian seasoning
other seasoning to taste
1 lb ground beef

Put cabbage, tomatoes (with juice), onion, and seasoning
in Dutch oven or large pot over low heat; cook and stir until
simmering.

Add ground beef on top; cover and cook. stirring occasionally,
about 45 minutes.

Do not pre-cook the beef.  Just stir it in, keeping the fat
for flavor.  The meat will cook through.

Serves 6
